{
  "texts": [
    "In this study, we explore the PTQ-QLoRA that integrates 4-bit post-training quantization with QLoRA to optimize the deployment of LLMs in resourcelimited environments.",
    "Through extensive experimentation, we demonstrate that this integration can match or surpass the performance of 16-bit full parameter fine-tuning, across various base LLMs, quantization methods and tasks.",
    "The results highlight that combining PTQ with QLoRA enhances model efficiency without sacrificing task-specific accuracy.",
    "This effective solution allows high-performing LLMs to be deployed with fewer resources.",
    "Overall, our findings underscore the potential of this integration to improve the practical deployment of LLMs, offering a scalable approach for future applications."
  ]
}